    "basic_qualifications": "- 3+ years of data engineering experience<br/>- 4+ years of SQL experience<br/>- Experience with data modeling, warehousing and building ETL pipelines<br/>- Experience with at least one programming language (Python, Java, Scala).<br/>- Proven ability to work with large-scale datasets and optimize performance",
